OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVariable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and a few showers
OL,7,Fthis evening. Then thickening cloud
OL,8,Fwill bring some occasional light rain
OL,9,Ffrom the southwest in the early hours.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FCloudy with occasional rain or
OL,12,Fdrizzle, this turning more persistent
OL,13,Ffor a time in the afternoon. Drier
OL,14,Facross Orkney later. Fresh southerly
OL,15,Fwinds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FOften
OL,18,Fcloudy with showers over the weekend.
OL,19,FFewer showers on Monday. Fresh to
OL,20,Fstrong west or southwesterly winds on
OL,21,FSaturday.
